title: Spyder Auto Installation: 350Z LED DRL Headlights (HID Version) + Bumper Removal
description: This video offers a step-by-step walkthrough of the installation process of a set of Spyder aftermarket headlights for Nissan 350Z models equipped with the HID headlamp option. Follow along as we remove and reinstall the front bumper fascia and connect these LED Daytime Running Light equipped headlights to the car's factory wiring harness. No cutting or wire splicing necessary.
tags: Spyder LED Headlights, how to install, Nissan 350Z, spyder lights, Z33, 350 Z
